column5: What can I say Joey?? You go girl!!
CONGRATULATIONS!!!!!!!!!!!!
Biteme, that avatar is just plain freaky  And ya, I'll try to get that cooler involved somehow, he he he!  Joey
Have fun with it Joey, they have an awesome camera crew and the people there are top notch. You'll have a blast I'm sure.  JP
sweeeet! that's cool...congrats!!!
Congrats!! Thats awesome!
Way to go girl!!! Congratulations.
Right on Monique!! Congratulations!!
Congrates girl.....last time I was on film it was at the local police station but thats another story. Have fun with it and try to get a copy for the Southern Contingincy to see.  Art
That is awesome news Marsha!  I mean Joey!     You must be soooo excited!  We can't wait to see your smilin' mug on TV!
Congrats Joey and good luck.  Have fun with it.
Congrats Joey!!!
Woops, your not Monique, your Joey!!
That's okay Sturgman, I was flattered by that statement  Joey

Congrats Joey! And to think I just met you a coupla weeks back and now your gonna be famous! Glad i was nice to you. Tell Tybo the wally's are bitin real fast and hard at the Q, he'll be gone from the house for sure! HH
A star in the making, congrats
Joey is already a star in my books. Good luck with the show Joey
YOU ROCK!!!!!  Congrats Joey!
Wow, that is so kewl!  Congrates to ya Joey and Tybo!  Now, Tybo, makes sure you get that den all spiffy for Joey will ya!
Very Cool!!  Hope we get to see a video of it on OFC when it's done!  Best of luck and have fun!  dk
Congrats Joey. I'll be watching the WFN for it when it hits the big screen and Good Luck to you.  Mike
Wow!  Congrats!  You should put in your contract that you won't eat any red M&M's and that you will only be interviewed whilst sitting in your cooler.  Good luck!!!

Huge Congrats Joey.........Huge!!!!!!!! We've been so busy I missed this post when it came out. WTG..dang your one lucky Gal..didnt you just win something else too..sheesh! You gotta be doing something right...the fish gods have been smiling on you. Pete
Ya know... Joey... do you have an agent / manager yet.. im available for 10%.....
Hel* I'll buy you for 10% TJ. Lets see thats what 2 litres Canadian right???  Art

Well, as some of you may remember, TJ put this thread on awhile ago  Casting Call  I got a call last week and they said they had narrowed the applicants down to 10 and they were going to decide on who to pick of those 10 (I believe they said 3 of the 10).  Well I got the call back today and they are coming to my house to shoot on Thursday.  Ill make sure I wear my OFC shirt or hat  WOOOHOOOO.  This is so exciting.  I'll let you all know what happens and when it will air.  Dang, now I gotta tidy up the house  Cheers  Joey
Cool.   You still gonna remember us peons when you are famous, lol?
you go girl    that so cool  good luck
Where you gonna hide Tybo when they show up????
And to think I shared the Niagara with you only a couple weeks back when you were just a mere OFNer  Don't forget us Joey, when you reach stardom with Izumi & Cronze
You go Joey, go.. whoo hooo  Thats so exciting....  Good luck...
Yep! We'll all be able to say we knew her way back when she used to scold suspended fish.
Man I knew him when he said there was no fish in the bay here,Heck even gave him a few spots to try.LMAO  WTG J.  Looking forward to the show.
Way cool Joey Good luck ,will be rooting for ya
hey ... you stole my post..  and Joey!!  That's just GREAT!!!  I can't wait!!!
fantastic news...I'm so proud (sniff, sniff)
Right on have fun!  Cheers1
Good stuff, very cool...
good luck joey....go get em.....  make us OFC"ers all proud
glad to hear it Joey, congrats, boston.
Thats way cool.Are you gonna have to sit in the cooler? Joe

That's great news Joey, I was hoping you would be the one    Someone's gotta represent us women folk   , I know you'll be great and have a blast....looking forward to seeing it....might even have to shell out the few bucks to get the sattelite upgrade now  Maureen
Thats awesome Joey,just tell Paul to go for a walk when they show up  Steve

Conrats Joey thats awesome, Awesome too that we have a woman who won.  Personally i don't think there is enough of us  woman folk on the fishing  tv  channels......  I am so jealous.. ...lol...But i hope you have a fantabulous time hon.
Thanks everyone.  I've just been busy "tidying up" the place.  And no worries, Paul has to work    I think he's a little camera shy anyhow  This is sure gonna be interesting.  Joey
Congrats Joey, have fun !!
....Spectacular! Congratulations to you Miss Joey.  Odd though, I can't stop thinking I read this somewhere before?
WTG Joey, have Tybo clean the house now that you are going to be a star.  Regards, Sam
Way to go girl !  I hope TJ gets the episode on tape/cd so us OFNers that don't get that show will get to watch you in action...
